        <div class="features">
            <div class="feature">
                <h3><span class="emoji">üõí</span>How It Works</h3>
                <ol>
                    <li><strong>Connect securely:</strong> Link your Farm to People account through our secure web form</li>
                    <li><strong>Text when ready:</strong> Send "plan" to our number when you want meal ideas</li>
                    <li><strong>Get personalized recipes:</strong> Receive AI-generated meal plans based on your actual cart contents</li>
                    <li><strong>Cook with confidence:</strong> Use every ingredient with detailed cooking guidance</li>
                </ol>
