            <div class="policy-highlight">
                This service sends SMS messages <strong>only in direct response to user requests</strong>. 
                No marketing, promotional messaging, or unsolicited communications.
            </div>
            
            <div class="policy-grid">
                <div class="policy-item">
                    <strong>üöÄ Opt-in Method</strong>
                    Text our number to start (examples: "hello", "plan", "new") or provide explicit verbal consent
                </div>
                <div class="policy-item">
                    <strong>üìÖ Message Frequency</strong>
                    On-demand/transactional only - messages sent only when you interact or request services
                </div>
                <div class="policy-item">
                    <strong>‚õî Opt-out Instructions</strong>
                    Reply "STOP" at any time to stop receiving messages. Reply "START" to re-enable
                </div>
                <div class="policy-item">
                    <strong>‚ùì Help Instructions</strong>
                    Reply "HELP" for assistance or contact information
                </div>
                <div class="policy-item">
