                    Phone numbers and messages used solely for meal planning. Data never sold or shared with third parties
                </div>
                <div class="policy-item">
                    <strong>üë• Age Requirement</strong>
                    Service intended for adults (18+). Must be legal age to use SMS services
                </div>
            </div>
            
