                    <span class="tech-item">FastAPI Web Framework</span>
                    <span class="tech-item">Playwright Browser Automation</span>
                    <span class="tech-item">OpenAI GPT-4</span>
                    <span class="tech-item">Supabase Database</span>
                    <span class="tech-item">SMS API Integration</span>
                    <span class="tech-item">Pandas Data Analysis</span>
                    <span class="tech-item">Real-time Web Scraping</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="use-case">
                <h3><span class="emoji">üéØ</span>Service Use Case</h3>
                <p><strong>Primary Function:</strong> Transactional meal planning automation for Farm to People customers</p>
                <br>
                <p><strong>User Journey:</strong></p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Customer places Farm to People order</li>
                    <li>Customer texts our service when ready to meal plan</li>
                    <li>AI analyzes cart contents and generates personalized recipes</li>
                    <li>Customer receives actionable meal plan via SMS</li>
                </ul>
                <br>
                <p><strong>Benefits:</strong> Reduces food waste, improves meal variety, saves planning time</p>
            </div>
        </div>

