            <p>For questions about this service, reply "HELP" via SMS or explore the project repository.</p>
            <br>
            <p><strong>GitHub Repository:</strong> 
                <a href="https://github.com/zoelsner/farmtopeople" target="_blank">
                    github.com/zoelsner/farmtopeople
                </a>
            </p>
            <br>
            <p><strong>Developer:</strong> Zachary Oelsner</p>
            <div class="disclaimer">
                This is a personal development project showcasing AI-powered automation, 
